window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Death is no problem in the Nightmare Realm. At least, it shouldn't have been.</b></p> <p>The dark place of sinister powers has its secrets. Between the rapidly multiplying population of monsters, demons slithering in the shadows, the Great God greedily guarding a world-shattering revelation, a mysterious dweller of the Nightmare Realm, and Neave and his companions, interests will collide, and war will be waged.</p> <p>Can they leave the realm prepared for the calamity waiting outside?</p> <p>More importantly, with an unknown manipulator lurking in the shadows and the insanity permeating the realm of nightmares...</p> <p>Will they stay in control of their minds?</p>"; 
